    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. This beauty has been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single weekend. It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust to be found! I'm sad to see it go, but I know it'll make the next owner so happy. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 45900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
